public class Dashboard
extends com.openfeint.internal.ui.WebNav

The Dashboard is your interface for opening up the OpenFeint Dashboard. Methods are provided to go to the root dashboard, as well as opening up to view specific Leaderboards, or the Achievements list for the current User.
